metadata.name: Red Temptation
metadata.description:
How enchanting and fascinating love can be!
It shakes up our lives and makes us curious about its new world with many facets. And when it is reciprocated, we feel overjoyed in our seventh heaven.

1/1 handpainted digital artwork, 2000 x 2000 px

Creator Barbara Johanna Billeiter alias Duckylemon.
